episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - Full Highlights - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Utah upsets #14 Stanford on the road 40-21. Tyler Huntley, Samson Nakua, and Zack Moss accounted for 3 offensive TD's and Jaylon Johnson returned an INT 100 yards to the house.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - TD Compilation - 10-6-18
episodes.description: 2 rush TD's from Zack Moss, a 100 yard Pick-6, and a long Tyler Huntley to Samson Nakua TD pass account for Utah's 4, 6-pointers tonight.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford -  4th Quarter highlights - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Utah shuts down Stanford's comeback bid, outscoring the Cardinal 13-0 in the final quarter. Final score: Utah 40 #14 Stanford 21

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 4th quarter Huntley to Nacua TD - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Tyler Huntley evades the Stanford Pressure and finds Samson Nakua for a huge game-sealing TD; Utah leads 37-21.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 3rd Quarter highlights - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Stanford makes a comeback, outscoring the Utes 14-3 in the quarter, but Utah still holds a 27-21 lead going into the 4th.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 2nd Quarter highlights - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Utah gets into the endzone twice more on a 100 yard pick-6 from Jaylon Johnson and Zack Moss' second rush TD of the night. They lead 24-7 at halftime.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 1st Quarter highlights - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Utah gets out in front early for the second straight week. They take a 7-0 lead on the road vs. #14 Stanford thanks to a usual stout defensive effort and another Zack Moss TD run.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 2nd quarter Zack Moss 2nd Rush TD - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Moss rips off another TD run on 4th down to extend Utah's lead to 21-0 late in the first half.

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - 2nd quarter Jaylon Johnson 100yd Int return TD - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Jaylon Johnson steps in front of a redzone pass from Stanford's KJ Costello; extends the lead to 14-0

episodes.title: Utah vs. Stanford - Zack Moss Rush TD - 10-6-18
episodes.description: Zack Moss finds the endzone as the Utes score first and take an early 7-0 lead on the road vs. #14 Stanford.
